ues, local models, Mac Studio setup, scaling]\n\n---\n\n## Recommended Videos from Alex Finn\n[Which videos cover which topics - for further learning]\n\n---\n\n**IMPORTANT:**\n- Read EVERY file completely - extract ALL key information\n- Synthesize the content - don't just list bullet points\n- Make it actionable - a real guide Bobby can use\n- Include specific commands, settings, tools mentioned\n- Flag anything that seems like an opinion vs fact\n- Save the final document with UTF-8 encoding"}],"timestamp":1774924489982}}
